Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.34,0:00:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OVERMAN KING-GAINER
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.12,0:01:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為布林西魯帝是\N很久以前的Overman
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.79,0:01:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以莎拉才無法完全說明清楚\N在那裡面得知的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.93,0:01:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是米亞還有Over Devil\N誰都不可能會知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.83,0:01:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為就連布林西魯帝最後\N使出的OverSkill
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.94,0:01:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也都還無法說明呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「化身 多米聶特」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.36,0:02:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只用一枚硬幣就\N一直贏到現在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對自衛團的哥哥來說\N這也是理所當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.47,0:02:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有挑戰者呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.13,0:02:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.24,0:02:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電玩冠軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.50,0:02:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛西亞，你之前很忙是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.31,0:02:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.21,0:02:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我因為工作的關係\N現在到了拜卡魯湖這來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.74,0:02:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.78,0:02:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也在拜卡魯湖附近的\N巨蛋都市國內喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.78,0:02:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要碰個面呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.38,0:02:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不知道我們\N能待在這待多久呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.62,0:02:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼忙的時候\N有人會去打電動嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.76,0:02:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.99,0:02:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.96,0:02:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，囉唆的人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.09,0:02:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.79,0:02:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉是...\N莎拉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，一個囉唆的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.47,0:02:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，我就是莎拉.可達瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.90,0:02:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.27,0:03:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過要是運氣夠好\N說不定可以碰到面喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟業者的交涉是由肯恩來做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.23,0:03:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣\N你也不能跑去打電動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.27,0:03:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們願意當我們的領航員了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.25,0:03:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是有聽過了啦\N沒想到竟然那麼大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.82,0:03:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好帶我們走\N冰比較厚的路線喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.52,0:03:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.72,0:03:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想沉到水裡去呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.79,0:03:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個凹凹凸凸的白色玩意\N是什麼東西呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.86,0:04:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山？就是真的山嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.97,0:04:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說這個湖水很小了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.44,0:04:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個湖水是南北走向的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.34,0:04:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要橫渡湖水\N山就會很礙事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.45,0:04:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為單位的引擎\N還無法爬上斜面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.68,0:04:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說它可以爬山嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.02,0:04:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們越過這湖泊之前\N我會讓引擎的性能提升的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.36,0:04:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越過山嶺呀...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要經過這種鄉下地方真是不方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.99,0:04:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要含著湯匙說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.63,0:04:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個壺的開口太小了\N我不經意就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.00,0:04:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.17,0:04:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去契茲的城堡\N「利曼」機器都市國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.37,0:04:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這條路線是最快的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.17,0:04:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.01,0:04:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因為\N對手是「黑色南十字星」嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.98,0:04:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,契茲他不是普通的鄉下人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.11,0:04:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖雷根的各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.88,0:04:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您們好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.15,0:04:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,契茲大人命令我要殲滅你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.42,0:05:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是被命令要來殲滅你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.46,0:05:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你們乖乖投降的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.23,0:05:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就不會攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.87,0:05:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你們乖乖投降就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.33,0:05:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有被她給瞧扁了嗎\N阿斯哈姆上尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.04,0:05:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管它是否真有這種實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.11,0:05:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體人員...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.31,0:05:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出擊是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.75,0:05:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把它打回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.95,0:05:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要出發的比上尉的葛雷姆還慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.15,0:05:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種虛張聲勢的Overman
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.26,0:05:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.69,0:05:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們乖乖投降就沒意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.30,0:05:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得我從東邊的海上\N大老遠跑到這裡來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.54,0:05:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.91,0:05:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.11,0:05:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要迷惘\N一口氣把她給解決掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.68,0:05:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.61,0:05:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼五百羅漢\N千人菩薩的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.92,0:06:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是Overman做得到的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.16,0:06:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你有多小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.96,0:06:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要用安德葛雷姆\NMach Bend Shaker
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.36,0:06:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不可能躲得掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.97,0:06:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還須要補給
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.27,0:06:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是外行人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.07,0:06:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,共振衝擊波？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.01,0:06:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.02,0:06:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Mach Bend Shaker吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.22,0:06:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣怎麼行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.26,0:06:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然吹飛了四台安德葛雷姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你躲也是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.59,0:07:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你們裝得有點聖雷根的程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.56,0:07:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像也沒個像樣的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你馬上回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.53,0:07:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是去看引擎而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.60,0:07:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇心旺盛也挺好的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.51,0:07:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒出去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.65,0:07:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫辛西亞的人不是在附近嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她聽見了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.52,0:07:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.59,0:07:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓋那這個年紀的男孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.09,0:07:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與其說打電動\N其實是想要和辛西亞一起玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.59,0:07:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種想法也不壞呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的，莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.43,0:07:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不出去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就請你用King Gainer\N去幫忙拉單位吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.47,0:07:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.80,0:08:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去幫忙好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德葛雷姆部隊全滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.65,0:08:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,札基，你逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.29,0:08:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要逃了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.89,0:08:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我當她的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.43,0:08:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去跟London IMA報告說\N西伯鐵的Overman
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.26,0:08:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向我們發起抵抗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.97,0:08:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個舉動確實是可看成\N背叛這個世界了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.64,0:08:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.18,0:08:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能讓札基看到我打輸的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.48,0:08:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管我們怎麼落魄\N聖雷根就是聖雷根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.15,0:08:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就好好領教我的實力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.49,0:08:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的武器還真有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.10,0:09:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我就可以逮到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.97,0:09:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.80,0:09:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次輪我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為這樣就可以\N讓我感到意外嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.95,0:09:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要以為用蠻力\N可以打贏葛雷姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛躲開的圓盤...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.43,0:09:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.24,0:09:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種Overman\N是西伯鐵獨立開發出來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.42,0:09:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他是有點骨氣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.82,0:09:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛西亞大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.05,0:09:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多貝克部隊到達了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.02,0:09:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.99,0:10:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要殺了聖雷根的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.43,0:10:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他們全體都回收吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.66,0:10:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像少了一台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.13,0:10:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不妙，不可以讓他逃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.74,0:10:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.08,0:10:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種部隊就算聖雷根\N的正規部隊的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.71,0:10:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓋那他還比較帶勁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.02,0:10:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那邊在戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.72,0:10:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.96,0:10:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少要數過子彈的數目再用呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.27,0:10:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能在這裡被幹掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.48,0:10:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撐下去呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.61,0:10:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要逃到水中去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.52,0:11:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.36,0:11:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又碰面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.40,0:11:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了這裡了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.03,0:11:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞邦的居住區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.93,0:11:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要笑得那麼輕薄啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.80,0:11:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是他們把冰上用的\N剪影引擎給打壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.97,0:11:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們才會坐在這種\N破爛剪影引擎上呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思\N我這台很「破爛」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.41,0:11:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去搭那個單位吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.45,0:11:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要比亞邦的居住區\N更早到達吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.95,0:11:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此\N你也想跟亞邦的五賢人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.55,0:11:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多搾一點油水吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.16,0:11:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你盡快往前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.49,0:11:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她到底是打哪來的\N旅行藝人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.97,0:11:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.83,0:11:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比剛剛更近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是西伯鐵在內哄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是他們打來這裡了\N你就把他們擋下來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.47,0:11:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.41,0:12:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要一小時就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.08,0:12:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.78,0:12:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.48,0:12:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動人美麗的貴夫人的請托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是高興的全身發抖呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.59,0:12:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好像不是內哄喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.23,0:12:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他們在戰鬥\N這是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.10,0:12:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是兩台Overman在互鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.27,0:12:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們的動法一點也不好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.24,0:12:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們好像在打破冰塊喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.40,0:12:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湖水中央的冰比較薄\N也是原因之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.91,0:12:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們又不能讓他們\N過度地破壞冰塊呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.44,0:12:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.78,0:12:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像來了台挺不錯的Overman
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.22,0:12:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.79,0:12:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.13,0:12:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我沒時間跟你瞎耗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.80,0:13:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拆掉我的關節了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.87,0:13:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會沉下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.71,0:13:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.14,0:13:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是開玩笑的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.55,0:13:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.49,0:13:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不會太慢了一點嗎？\N高烏力隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.79,0:13:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.93,0:14:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不知道Overman的戰鬥\N打破了多少的冰塊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.73,0:14:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉，接過公主殿下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.20,0:14:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.84,0:14:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.27,0:14:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.58,0:14:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？它不在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.58,0:14:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣\N你們也不知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.82,0:14:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳思它...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.95,0:14:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安娜公主，你不可以去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.52,0:14:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.52,0:14:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去找琳思才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.19,0:14:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找琳思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.49,0:14:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公主請跟莎拉小姐\N一起避難去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.09,0:14:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...\N琉波芙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.59,0:14:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公主就拜託你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.93,0:14:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉波芙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.40,0:14:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬馬度\N不用連你也去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.73,0:14:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可真傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.60,0:14:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個大男人竟然在追\N家教老師呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.24,0:14:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.47,0:14:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.94,0:14:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說要在冰噴起的地方\N跟亞邦之間設下防衛線嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.78,0:14:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要設下防衛線嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.98,0:14:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Gainer也沒有行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.89,0:14:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水中的Overman的行動\N相當的激烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.22,0:15:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓單位的速度\N提高一點嗎？貝洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.16,0:15:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在試了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.43,0:15:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉波芙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.76,0:15:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳思\N你在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.00,0:15:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳思...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.04,0:15:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉波芙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.17,0:15:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.41,0:15:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒聽見嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.84,0:15:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.48,0:15:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.44,0:15:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.65,0:15:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它在吊艙的上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.96,0:15:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它為什麼跑到那個地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.52,0:15:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬馬度老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.69,0:15:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.13,0:15:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？貝洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.86,0:15:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於出現在雷達上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.96,0:15:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,類似西伯鐵的剪影引擎的傢伙\N也正在移動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.17,0:15:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓋那，去阻止前方那奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.50,0:15:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它好像正在對你虎視眈眈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.14,0:15:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是這樣沒錯\N但那是什麼東西呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.51,0:15:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是普通的雞蛋喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.31,0:15:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了\N真是天真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.58,0:16:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比巧克力更甜啊\N(甜跟天真同音)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.55,0:16:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙變形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.23,0:16:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速度就是你的OverSkill 嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.53,0:16:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就讓你瞧瞧\N多米聶特的力量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.51,0:16:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被它當成玩具在耍了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.49,0:16:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那台Overman是什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.73,0:16:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種招式竟然會是\N它的OverSkill
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.43,0:16:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要太囂張了，怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.65,0:17:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙...\N竟然做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.55,0:17:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腳下的冰就要碎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,升降機又故障了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是倒霉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.42,0:17:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬馬度先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.72,0:17:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用擔心\N在那邊等我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吊艙的左邊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.57,0:17:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那台剪影引擎是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.21,0:17:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬馬度大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.62,0:17:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉波芙\N我抓到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.59,0:17:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒人掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.19,0:17:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請確認自 己左右的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.82,0:17:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那台剪影引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.89,0:17:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓋那，你在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.43,0:17:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過是台剪影引擎\N還敢在這給我囂張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.37,0:18:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要瞧不起人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.98,0:18:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那手臂是什麼東西？\N是Overman的手臂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.95,0:18:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然強脫人家衣服\N這連我都不會幹呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.53,0:18:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓋那，快去追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.93,0:18:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.67,0:18:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,單位那邊不要緊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.74,0:18:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對\N我也很擔心那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.47,0:18:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.44,0:18:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.35,0:18:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被噁心的傢伙給摸到了\N真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.42,0:18:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那邊的Overman\N也是有優點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.92,0:18:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會讓人有想要用用看的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.03,0:19:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水面有冰塊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.24,0:19:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的\N這裡有柵欄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.94,0:19:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.47,0:19:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我不一個人跑出來的話\N就不會變成這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.74,0:19:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.94,0:19:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我知道我也能為你貢獻\N一己之力時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.58,0:19:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這喜悅感令我感到了無比的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.92,0:19:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果您這麼說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.19,0:19:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我的幸福感就是你的\N三倍...五倍...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不！是十倍呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.69,0:19:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉波芙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.93,0:19:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬馬度老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.57,0:19:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.57,0:19:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉波芙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.28,0:20:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,單位被拉回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.09,0:20:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是Overman呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N就算沒有「胸罩」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.53,0:20:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要拉單位也是輕而易舉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.40,0:20:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上岸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.83,0:20:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，快拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.41,0:20:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼纜就麻煩你們固定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.94,0:20:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.01,0:20:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是琉波芙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.38,0:20:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有馬馬度也下去了\N到現在還沒回來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.89,0:21:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.02,0:21:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.79,0:21:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓋那，下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.39,0:21:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「下面」...\N你是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.83,0:21:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.17,0:21:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它是在說「跟我過去」嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.11,0:21:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.32,0:21:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現了馬馬度跟琉波芙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.49,0:21:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過他們的身體都泡在水中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.92,0:21:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.82,0:21:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們的水浸泡在水中...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.26,0:21:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上把他們救出來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.03,0:21:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.30,0:21:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒膽的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.23,0:21:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.67,0:21:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的水溫不是冰點以下的水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.57,0:21:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.94,0:21:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能是兩人的愛之力\N讓它變熱水的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.28,0:22:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為單位的光子墊造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.88,0:22:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用King Gainer的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.21,0:22:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他們撈起來後\N再把他們的身體弄暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.98,0:22:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用肌肉引擎的熱量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.83,0:22:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你醒來了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.07,0:22:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬馬度老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.57,0:22:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.47,0:22:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.58,0:22:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.68,0:22:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉波芙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.65,0:22:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.09,0:22:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得不是很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.42,0:22:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓋那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.26,0:22:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說琉波芙跟馬馬度都得救了
